goterms.name: negative regulation of immune effector process
goterms.description: Any process that stops, prevents, or reduces the frequency, rate, or extent of an immune effector process.

goterms.name: positive regulation of immune effector process
goterms.description: Any process that activates or increases the frequency, rate, or extent of an immune effector process.
